name: NutritionOrderItemGrouping
title: Nutrition Order Item Grouping
description: Enteral Products are included in a separate value set.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values are items which represent nutrition and diet orders for patients in the acute care setting.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of these data elements is to identify specific nutrition/diet orders that are selected to provide nutrition interventions based upon patient problems.),(Inclusion Criteria: Data included are Food and Nutrient Delivery, Vitamin and Mineral Supplement and Bioactive Substance Management and Parenteral Nutrition Management.),(Exclusion Criteria: This set does not include modular and/or enteral products.)
